subject: Football (College)
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Blake Bortles passed for one touchdown and ran for another, helping No. 17 Central Florida dominate visiting Rutgers, 41-17, to remain unbeaten in the American Athletic Conference.
